Privacy Policy for Counter 4 AM

At Counter 4 AM, we prioritize the privacy and security of our users. This Privacy Policy outlines the information collected and used by the Counter 4 AM app, and how it is handled. By using the Counter 4 AM app, you consent to the terms of this Privacy Policy.

Information Collection and Use
1.1. Personal Information: Counter 4 AM does not collect any personally identifiable information from its users. We do not require users to provide any personal information, such as names, email addresses, or phone numbers, to use the app.

1.2. Usage Data: The app may collect certain non-personal information automatically, such as the device's operating system version, app version, and other anonymous usage statistics. This data is used for analytical purposes to improve the app's performance and user experience. It does not personally identify individual users.

Data Storage
2.1. Local Storage: Counter 4 AM utilizes the Sqflite library to store counter information locally on the user's device. This information includes counter names, values, and other related data. All data is stored securely on the user's device and is not transmitted or synced with any external server or database.

Advertising
3.1. Advertisements: Counter 4 AM displays advertisements served by AdMob, a third-party advertising network owned by Google. AdMob may collect and use certain anonymous information about user interactions with the ads displayed in the app for the purpose of delivering more relevant advertisements.

3.2. Third-Party Links: Counter 4 AM may contain links to external websites or services that are not owned or controlled by us. We are not responsible for the privacy practices or the content of such third-party websites or services.

Changes to this Privacy Policy
5.1. We reserve the right to modify or update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be effective upon posting the revised Privacy Policy within the Counter 4 AM app. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any updates.

Contact Us
6.1. If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or the practices of the Counter 4 AM app, please contact us at prodesignamcontact@gmail.com.
